{"tid":271791,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"三居屋屋苑逾2000伙 傳最快本月22日攪珠","createTime":"2017-06-05T10:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T17:02:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b5e0633be638f66003c987aedfeaa85d983f9e","tid":271791,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"2017年6月5日 18:43上一篇<br />\n據市場消息指房委會於今年3月底以市價七折推售彩虹彩興苑、梅窩銀河苑及銀蔚苑,房委會有望最快於本月22日進行攪珠揀樓,惟有關日期尚待官方確認。<br />\n<br />\n房委會今年3月下旬以市價七折推售彩虹彩興苑、梅窩銀河苑及銀蔚苑共2,057個單位，加上36個因個人或經濟問題取消買賣協議單位，共提供2,093個單位。<br />\n<br />\n3個屋苑單位面積368至552平方呎，售價約139萬至385萬元，最快明年8月至2019年3月落成。<br />\n<br />\n是次居屋綠白表比例為五比五，另預留100個配額予單身申請者,而揀樓次序仍以長者家庭優先、其次為一般家庭，最後為1人申請者。根據過往程序，攪珠儀式將在樂富客務中心舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/1829254/三居屋屋苑逾2000伙%20傳最快本月22日攪珠\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1829254%2F%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E5%B1%8B%E8%8B%91%E9%80%BE2000%E4%BC%99%2520%E5%82%B3%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%8822%E6%97%A5%E6%94%AA%E7%8F%A0&d=ywAjMil7f7dk0WmdcD32rIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9ed76121\" target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/1829254/三居屋屋苑逾2000伙%20傳最快本月22日攪珠</a>"},{"pid":"5006be47d5d23abb4a38a0924bef799270646a2c","tid":271791,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"139萬係咩單位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea6358823065c481863963c9d091527b292eb1db","tid":271791,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>139萬係咩單位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樓西北垃圾房好似係"},{"pid":"dd3cc9c3fb06627b79762138b52d544204b6d617","tid":271791,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>139萬係咩單位黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一樓